{"tid":277711,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食牛腩河食到比人笑","createTime":"2017-06-09T23:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T07:24:56.000Z","uid":32462,"like":18,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6a96a2be3ecb14c64e991d2feacf2dc028053c0","tid":277711,"uid":32462,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T23:49:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的前排去咗鄉下仔魚蛋檔嗌咗碗我最鍾意嘅牛腩河食，點知個日啲肉特別鞋食到我痴哂牙好唔舒服，最後食完梗係要搵枝牙籤挑吓<br />\n<br />\n跟住我一邊玩電話一邊拎住個牙籤樽係咁chock，點知chock極都chock唔到一枝牙籤，跟住我望一望隻手，屌你老母成手胡椒粉嘅？！頓時四周傳黎一陣恥笑聲，好彩我靈機一觸，即刻學salt bae咁落啲胡椒粉落食完碗牛腩河到，再一啖湯跟住9秒9飛身埋單走人！<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得我反應係咪好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好型<br />\n負評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好柒"},{"pid":"c62a779d74d07cec2035780078d36a6407ab54e9","tid":277711,"uid":83813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T23:51:26.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"3fad947e7b2e8f3d5f0121b877bada8a271c0db5","tid":277711,"uid":119066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T00:02:56.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"3c9496b26f670bd7f9a22108610826df91512037","tid":277711,"uid":46631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:09:53.000Z","msg":"咁你有冇salt bae咁型?"},{"pid":"5db40ba9ec51e01a0da50dfda6ddc6976d7f6cda","tid":277711,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:19:31.000Z","msg":"呀"},{"pid":"2d1e185ed93e4c74f22d46aa3601c573ffbc5fe1","tid":277711,"uid":38744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:22:25.000Z","msg":"仲以為你會好似食白粉咁一野索晒佢<br />\n咁先夠霸氣"},{"pid":"1be88d130c0dac17d601464b25b853852d3e8ce3","tid":277711,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:23:39.000Z","msg":"超級憨膠膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15320fcb9781b7cdee1a790c1624fd53dec5b497","tid":27